Post-Deployment Steps – Field Service Mobile Settings

Navigate to Field Service Mobile Settings in Salesforce Setup.

Clone the existing setting:

Name: Field service Guest User Portal

Developer Name: FieldServiceGuestUserPortal

In the cloned setting:

Locate the checkbox “Send appointment notification on assignment”

Uncheck this checkbox

Save the setting.

Assign the setting to the Guest User profile:

Open the newly created Field service Guest User Portal setting

Click Assign to Profiles

Select the profile Scheduled Appointments Calendar Profile

Click Change Assignment

Choose Assign new settings

Save the changes
